---
title: "Why Silent Automation Failures Are Draining Revenue You Cannot See"
date: "2024-11-25"
summary: "Silent automation failures drain revenue through wrong outputs that nobody catches. Build detection mechanisms that surface what the automation gets wrong."
coverImage: ""
tags:
